# Hyphen-group

## DevOps Engineer practical test

Please answer all questions. Use the tools / languages you find most confident in.

### Section 1 - CI 

1. Using GitHub and GitHub actions build a docker container. (The docker container should contain an API server which can be used for part two)

2. When a contributor creates a PR, please run tests and report results.

### Section 2 - CD

1. When a tag is created please add release notes.

2. After release notes have been added use Terraform to deploy the container to Kubernetes.